name: Mallorie Cook
text: Cant ever eat here. Last time they gave us a completely raw pizza and the girl argued with me and said that it wasnt when the dough was completely raw. Made the mistake of going back after that, different people and somehow the dough was still way undercooked. Not going back this time.

name: Bethany Poole
text: Good food just a little long getting it.

name: Marc Bupp
text: I didn't visit Pizza Inn last week, or even last month!
